statements: SELECT * FROM palm_vein_recognition_reports;
SELECT user_id, report_date, accuracy_score FROM palm_vein_recognition_reports WHERE user_id = 100;
SELECT report_id, accuracy_score, report_date, user_id FROM palm_vein_recognition_reports ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM palm_vein_recognition_reports WHERE accuracy_score > 90;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(report_id) AS total_reports FROM palm_vein_recognition_reports GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_reports > 5;
SELECT * FROM palm_vein_recognition_reports WHERE user_id = 1 ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT user_id, AVG(accuracy_score) AS average_score FROM palm_vein_recognition_reports GROUP BY user_id HAVING AVG(accuracy_score) > 90;
SELECT report_id, user_id, report_date, accuracy_score FROM palm_vein_recognition_reports WHERE accuracy_score >= 80 ORDER BY accuracy_score DESC, report_date ASC;
SELECT user_id, MAX(accuracy_score) AS highest_score, MIN(accuracy_score) AS lowest_score FROM palm_vein_recognition_reports GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(report_id) AS num_reports FROM palm_vein_recognition_reports GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY num_reports DESC, user_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM reports_on_palm_vein_accuracy;
SELECT accuracy_score, report_date, patient_id FROM reports_on_palm_vein_accuracy ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT patient_name, patient_id FROM patients WHERE patient_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT AVG(accuracy_score) AS average_accuracy FROM reports_on_palm_vein_accuracy;
SELECT patient_name, patient_id FROM patients ORDER BY patient_name ASC;
SELECT report_id, patient_id, accuracy_score, report_date FROM reports_on_palm_vein_accuracy WHERE accuracy_score > 0.9 ORDER BY report_date DESC
SELECT * FROM reports_on_palm_vein_accuracy WHERE report_id = 1
SELECT patient_name, palm_vein_data FROM patients WHERE patient_id = 1001

SELECT user_id, COUNT(log_id) AS log_count FROM report_logs GROUP BY user_id HAVING log_count > 5;
SELECT user_id, user_name, email FROM user_details WHERE palm_vein_registered = TRUE ORDER BY user_name DESC;
SELECT r.user_id, r.report_date, l.log_data FROM report_logs l JOIN user_details d ON l.user_id = d.user_id JOIN palm_vein_recognition_accuracy r ON d.user_id = r.user_id;
